25:48.004 --> 25:49.965
I shouldn't have been
listening to the liquor.

25:50.382 --> 25:54.177
It's proof enough, shit, that liquor
doesn't know shit about horses!

25:55.136 --> 25:56.596
Look, Randy.

25:56.680 --> 25:59.766
I don't wanna fight with you, bud,
just open up the door.

26:00.433 --> 26:02.018
Randy, I'll tell you what.

26:02.102 --> 26:03.770
Let me in and...

26:04.396 --> 26:07.440
I'll let you take care
of the money from now on.

26:08.942 --> 26:10.277
You promise, sir?

26:10.360 --> 26:13.196
Yeah, I promise. Cross my heart
and hope to die, Randers.

26:13.280 --> 26:15.031
-All the money?
-All the money.

26:15.115 --> 26:16.241
All of it?

26:16.491 --> 26:17.993
You can take care of it.

26:18.076 --> 26:19.619
And I'll tell you what else I'll do.

26:19.703 --> 26:22.163
I'll give you a nice little
foot massage, Randers.

26:22.247 --> 26:23.415
And I'll, uh...

26:23.498 --> 26:25.208
I'll clean out your belly button

26:25.292 --> 26:28.420
with a nice, soft toothbrush
and some lavender.

26:28.753 --> 26:29.879
[lock clicking]

26:33.049 --> 26:34.884
-Thanks, Randy.
-Okay, Mr. Lahey.

26:36.011 --> 26:37.012
Boop, boop!

26:37.429 --> 26:38.471
[giggling]

26:38.555 --> 26:42.892
Ricky, Mike fucking Holmes couldn't
redo that bathroom for 200 bucks.

26:42.976 --> 26:45.145
-Like, what are you thinking?
-You don't understand, man.

26:45.228 --> 26:47.605
My head's got it mapped out in a way
that I'm still going to come

26:47.689 --> 26:51.151
